diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
index bf60e14..a4f34f9 100644
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -57,7 +57,7 @@ Use [PostCSS Nesting] as a plugin:
 
 ```js
 postcss([
-	require('postcss-nesting')({ /* options */ })
